much more useful if it allowed you to load a ROM directly into the Retron 5</div><br />I think the reason it doesn't take ROMs is to keep Hyperkin from getting <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lik_Sang" class="postlink">Lik Sang'd</a>. By having the machine rely exclusively on the cart slots, Hyperkin can rely on the essential copy defense, codified as 17 USC 117(a)(1) and foreign counterparts.

		

